{"tid":1170862,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭峰肯定係金庸小說入面最有魅力嘅男主角","createTime":"2019-05-25T09:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T04:35:24.000Z","uid":185990,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e5740ea8991d55cb6f168b20dbbbc6792951916c","tid":1170862,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"今日忍唔住翻睇返天龍八部，睇返蕭峰聚賢莊血戰群雄，喺少室山屌打游坦之、丁春秋同慕容復，喺雁門關前脅逼遼王一生唔可以攻打大宋，真係睇到好撚熱血！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住再睇佢中康敏詭計誤傷阿朱，結局又因為愧對遼王而自盡，睇到我好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武功舉世無雙、智勇相全、用情專一、行俠仗義......基本上集齊晒金庸小說所有主角嘅優點。所以蕭峰係金庸小說最有魅力嘅男主角，楊過、令狐沖、郭靖、張無忌全部要行埋一邊。<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64b5139da0300e1d0e0a06524b1e70bb4e33a78","tid":1170862,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"阿杰先係"},{"pid":"05b5975a136a20179ee4caac45088847bce1ace7","tid":1170862,"uid":185990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d64b5139da0300e1d0e0a06524b1e70bb4e33a78","tid":1170862,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"阿杰先係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b22c32d130c4d127ec249fe41973420a8011c07","tid":1170862,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"楊逍"},{"pid":"4f8df1711e0a51b9262bed95a37435157ea9ab27","tid":1170862,"uid":142872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"不服來辯"},{"pid":"f4bec7e55d56922987406a77559a3396444813ae","tid":1170862,"uid":185990,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0b22c32d130c4d127ec249fe41973420a8011c07","tid":1170862,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike